Saute beef in Spectrum Organic Extra Virgin Olive Oil over a high heat in a heavy bottom high sided pan. When browned all over remove and transfer to a plate. Season vegetables with Hain Pure Foods Iodized Sea Salt and pepper and saute until tender. Stir in Imagine Organic Beef Cooking Stock, wine, herbs, spices and beef. Bring to a boil, then reduce heat and simmer until beef is cooked through and tender about 20 minutes.